软件包 mobios.dist

接口摘要
Metric Metric is a distance oracle.
WeightMatrix A WeightMatrix is the substitution matrix of an Alphabetof Symbol objects.
 

类摘要
CountedMetric Wrapper around a base Metric that counts the invocations of Metric.getDistance(IndexObject,IndexObject).
ImageMetric Computes the distance between images.
LMetric This class computes the L family distance function on two vectors.
MSMetric MSDataMetric implements the Metric interface.
MSMSConstants Constant static default values for building indices on mass spectrometer data Code uses these as default, "tolerance" etc. also configurable via constructors.
MSMSMetric MSMSMetric is an implementation of a fuzzy cosine distance metric for comparing tandem spectra signatures.
SequenceFragmentMetric Computes distance on two Fragments.
SymmetricSubstitutionWeightMatrix Implements a WeightMatrix by providing a symmetric substitution matrix of double distances for a given Alphabet.
WHDGlobalFragmentMetric This class computes global alignment with weighted Hamming distance
WHDGlobalSequenceFragmentMetric Computes global alignment on Fragments with Weighted Hamming Distance
